thread.title: BRIEF-Jinfa Labi Maternity and Baby Articles amends FY 2017 net profit outlook

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Jinfa Labi Maternity and Baby Articles amends FY 2017 net profit outlook

organizations.name: jinfa labi maternity & baby articles co ltd

text:
Jan 30(Reuters) - Jinfa Labi Maternity & Baby Articles Co Ltd :
* Says net profit for FY 2017 to be 87.3 million yuan to 101.9 million yuan
* Says in the previous outlook, the company expected the net profit for FY 2017 to be 87.3 million yuan
* Says the net profit of FY 2016 was 72.8 million yuan
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/X6iVzQ
